title: Jennifer Hanson - Jennifer Hanson
description:
Singer-songwriter, and former Miss California Jennifer Hanson, released her self titled debut album in February 2003. Three singles were taken from the album,
&#039;Beautiful Goodbye&#039;, &#039;This Far Gone&#039; and &#039;Half A Heart Tattoo&#039;. Since the release of this album, Jennifer has released two further singles, &#039;Joyride&#039; in 2007, and &#039;73 (Everything Changes)&#039; earlier this year (2008), there was also a Christmas version of &#039;Joyride&#039; called &#039;Santa&#039;s Toy Ride&#039; which was posted in December 2007.
Apparently a new album is planned, but so far no details of a title or release date are available.
